-->	      <p><span class="first">Nxtbook Media</span> brings new media solutions to publishers, marketers, and clients in every industry vertical. In 2003 Nxtbook Media was one of the first companies to bring a full-service digital publication platform to the marketplace, helping content creators make their publications available to more readers via the power of the Web, and later via smartphone and tablet devices.</p>
<p>Since then, Nxtbook Media has been named an <span class="second">Inc 500 company</span> and remained at the top of the <span class="second">Best Places to Work in PA</span> list for several years. Nxtbook Media offers digital solutions to meet a wide breadth of needs, empowering brands of all sizes to grow their digital influence and audience. Top solutions can be broken into the following categories:</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>apps • digital replicas of print publications • responsive design<br />
publications &amp; websites • marketing services • custom solutions</strong></p>
<p>Within these categories is a plethora of experience, and outside of them are customized solutions created for specific clients with specific needs. Click to explore some of Nxtbook Media’s previous work, or <a href="tel:+18662681219"><span class="second">give us a call</span></a> to see what we can create to make your best goals reality.</p>

          

